imdb.plot outline: Oahu Party Bus is a Hawaiian reality television series that portrayed a family own Party Bus Company in Honolulu Hawaii and the lives of the owners Stacie and Gene Simeona, who became successful from their family-operated business, The series depicts the staff's interactions with customers and their drama situations around each bus ride, while following the interpersonal conflicts among the cast.
imdb.title: Oahu Party Bus
plot: _Oahu Party Bus_ (qv) is a Hawaiian reality television series that portrayed a family own Party Bus Company in Honolulu Hawaii and the lives of the owners Stacie and Gene Simeona, who became successful from their family-operated business, The series depicts the staff's interactions with customers and their drama situations around each bus ride, while following the interpersonal conflicts among the cast.
